overview: "I Am Aubrey" combines backstage footage, penetrating interviews and hardcore sex scenes lensed by four top filmmakers to expose stunning TS superstar Aubrey Kate. With a beautiful, bewitching face and a busty figure, the platinum blonde oozes glamour, but we get a look at the humor, pain and real-life challenges behind the impeccable makeup, sumptuous wardrobe and seductive sexuality.
title: I Am Aubrey
